elationen von Mensch und Umgebung nach.  aLandscaping esthetics in the relation between nature and culture: What effects does landscaping have on the human condition, perception and actions?  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 4aHiddensee. 4aKunst. 4aKunstgeschichte. 4aKunsttheorie. 4aKunstwissenschaft. 4aKünstlerische Forschung. 4aLandschaft. 4aNatur. 4aWeimar. 4aÄsthetik. 7aART / Criticism.2bisacsh  aAesthetics.  aArt History.  aArt.  aArtistic Research.  aFine Arts.  aHiddensee.  aLandscape.  aNature.  aTheory of Art.  aWeimar.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2017z978311071954308iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Architecture and Design 2017z9783110547719oZDB-23-DAD08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2017z9783110540550oZDB-23-DGG40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783839439043zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839439043423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783839439043/original  a978-3-11-071954-3  DG Plus eBook-Package 2017b2017  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_AD  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DADb2017  aZDB-23-DGGb2017